msgctxt "drawprinteroptions|extended_tip|distributeonmultiple"
msgid "Prints a large format document, such as a poster or banner, by distributing the document page across multiple sheets of paper. The distribution option calculates how many sheets of paper are needed. You can then piece together the sheets."
msgstr "ພິມເອກະສານຂະໜາດໃຫຍ່ ເຊັ່ນ ໂປສເຕີ ຫຼື ປ້າຍໂຄສະນາ ໂດຍການກະຈາຍໜ້າເອກະສານໄປໃສ່ເຈ້ຍຫຼາຍແຜ່ນ. ຕົວເລືອກການກະຈາຍຈະຄິດໄລ່ຈຳນວນເຈ້ຍທີ່ຈຳເປັນ. ຈາກນັ້ນ ທ່ານສາມາດເອົາເຈ້ຍແຕ່ລະແຜ່ນມາຕໍ່ໃສ່ກັນໄດ້."

#. kAHyQ
#: sd/uiconfig/sdraw/ui/drawprinteroptions.ui:260
msgctxt "drawprinteroptions|tilesheet"
msgid "Tile sheet of paper with repeated pages"
msgstr "ພິມແບບລຽງຕໍ່ກັນດ້ວຍໜ້າທີ່ຊ້ຳກັນ"

#. dBYC3
#: sd/uiconfig/sdraw/ui/drawprinteroptions.ui:269
msgctxt "drawprinteroptions|extended_tip|tilesheet"
msgid "Specifies that pages are to be printed in tiled format. If the pages are smaller than the paper, the page will be repeated multiple times on one sheet of paper."
msgstr "ກຳນົດວ່າໃຫ້ພິມໜ້າໃນຮູບແບບການປູກະເບື້ອງ (tiled format). ຖ້າໜ້າເອກະສານມີຂະໜາດນ້ອຍກວ່າເຈ້ຍ, ໜ້ານັ້ນຈະຖືກພິມຊ້ຳຫຼາຍໆ ເທື່ອໃນເຈ້ຍແຜ່ນດຽວ."

